➜面包糠炸西葫芦猪肉丸子的家常做法，简单好做，美味之极
http://www.sohu.com/a/416733593_119132	39411
<p class="ql-align-justify">以前胃口不好时，老妈会做一道醋熘西葫芦，酸香可口，总能打开食欲。以前我也认为，西葫芦就这一种做法，虽然味道不错，吃多了也会有一些厌烦。终于有一次，吃到了西葫芦炸丸子，味道相当不错。今天把详细做法教给大家，快来看看吧。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">面包糠炸西葫芦猪肉丸子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200906/da8b6d7c8ffa44938f44548626404d55.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">准备食材：猪肉馅200g 西葫芦1个 鸡蛋2个（实际用量1个） 淀粉50g 面包糠100g葱花5g 姜末5g</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200906/4f16a6b7be124cd1aba27640d9f6f776.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">制作方法：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1、首先把西葫芦用擦丝器擦成丝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200906/425cb2c7044c4e8dac85e3439c6407f2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify">2、放入2g盐腌出水分攥干剁碎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200906/f433af505aa54d199a92ec6553a8357b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3、把肉馅和西葫芦碎装进碗中放入2g盐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200906/275a7715d04543b18159d8650b145854.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">4、放入葱花和姜末</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200906/f8ee97dafec24ff2b842d7be7f8b2172.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">5、放入2g味精</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200906/1a865cbfcf734cfe869d6a9e675a0f86.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6、放入2g鸡精</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200906/c68cc67320954fc5ad881e5bb1ad9872.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">7、放入2g十三香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200906/3b85f1c7bec245c5ad9a74a06ce2af7e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">8、再磕入1个鸡蛋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200906/8f8acd6b212544f4b30f12f183c9223a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">9、放入淀粉搅拌均匀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200906/fd2c25ec387e485ca8fc0b7d9932bf3b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">10、把肉馅团成圆球放入盘中滚几下，使其沾满面包糠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200906/cf6ef9ad85544c0584f2d3f600075f83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">11、油锅烧热，油温6——7热放入肉团</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200906/b2e4f19aae1d480895fbbf23a734efe8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">12、小火炸制金黄熟透捞出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200906/b738d51ff719472cafa7a4daa2b90706.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">13、出锅，制作完成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200906/906d0c2204404a01b8cbc699550d1bae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>